==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Erucic
<hw>E*ru"cic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or derived from, a genus of cruciferous
Mediterranean herbs (<gen>Eruca</gen> or <gen>Brassica</gen>); <as>as,
<ex>erucic</ex> acid, a fatty acid resembling oleic acid, and found in
colza oil, mustard oil, etc.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Erucifrom</ent>⟦br⟧
